{"tid":1746801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與制度暴力割蓆，全部人出去投票","createTime":"2019-11-23T02:26:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T10:45:07.000Z","uid":16025,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"168d7a8516b5232d1435e5f89279012c5c4aafa7","tid":1746801,"uid":16025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:26:03.000Z","msg":"哩鋪真係要割蓆啦！<br />\n<br />\n一人一票，由區議會做起。<br />\n<br />\n你地唔出黎投票，美國人權法有雙普選有撚用啊?<br />\n<br />\n又想射落海投白票啊? 我屌你啦<br />\n<br />\n又想焦土啊? 我屌你啦<br />\n<br />\n全方位抗爭，用選票發聲，再街路抗爭，一日未完成，一日不放棄。<br />\n<br />\n聽日唔得閒投?我屌你啦<br />\n<br />\n政治冷感? 我屌你啦<br />\n<br />\n理大手足18歲以上想投都無得投，你唔投，邊個去投<br />\n<br />\n總之就去投票啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38027bebf4072e9293d8999d225731fc1e53d3c4","tid":1746801,"uid":16025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:29:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3f858cce24b204e53346b813ac011cd35f27c4c4","tid":1746801,"uid":16025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:25:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f69870e5e6a41d0c7a80181e8de9414136de393c","tid":1746801,"uid":24168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:28:57.000Z","msg":"各自努力<br />\n<br />\n勿中奸計"},{"pid":"43662d1938030c632dc02cb7c74e134faea638c0","tid":1746801,"uid":16025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:53:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"744076aa4ab1f9e303014cdc3fd3e41164f79f54","tid":1746801,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:53:29.000Z","msg":"**** 眾籌 ****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(由於中大民調欠缺資金做今次反送中民調，我們的眾籌會同時加入新項目，籌到的款項亦會用作資助中大民調)<